      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "We're not going to invent _another_ protocol for this.\n\nIf HTTP JSON-RPC longpolling does not provide a solution, then the stratum protocol would be the next natural community-adopted candidate.  Line-based JSON-RPC, whether client or server may send asynchronously, seems a fair match.\n",
      "user": {
        "login": "jgarzik",
