      "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body": "stratum has nothing to do with protocol buffers.  It is a protocol that is _less complex_ than HTTP, even:\n\n```\nC: JSON-RPC \\n\nS: JSON-RPC \\n\nC: JSON-RPC \\n\nS: JSON-RPC \\n\nS: JSON-RPC \\n\n```\n\nNo HTTP headers, no HTTP chunking, etc.  Very simple and easy: just text lines of JSON.  Client _or_ server may send a line at any time.\n",
